      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "N≥6 test specimens per configuration; specimens drawn from production lot representative of design intent.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated constructs tested across two laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5). All screws drawn from the same production lot as the CMM-characterized specimens. Inter-laboratory variability assessed; pooled CV = 4.3%. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
