      "rationale": "Three QoIs evaluated: stiffness (E/uval = 0.87, error 2.0%), yield force (E/uval = 1.31, error 2.4%), force at 40 mm (E/uval = 0.93, error 1.8%). All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. Gradation 2 achieved."
