      "rationale": "Validation specimens are the same non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw design as in the COU. ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard for this device class. Loading mode (compression-bending) is the primary clinical failure mode. High relevance confirmed. Gradation 2 achieved."
